data.description: Welcome to 3164 22nd St! This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has been recently remodeled and is full of charm. Featuring a modern galley kitchen with ample cabinet space, a partially finished basement, 2 car garage and more! Step inside and you're greeted with a large living room, a modern bathroom and one of the bedrooms. Upstairs you will find plenty of storage space in the 2 additional bedrooms and an office. Newer furnace, HWT and AC. Schedule your tour today! Back on the market at no fault of its own!!
